.deveronvale.co.uk/single-post/2018/06/18/Craig-Stewart-Appointed-Assistant-Manager Craig Stewart appointed Assistant Manager], ''Deveronvale Football Club'', 18 June 2018, Accessed 7 January 2019</ref>\n* Player/Goalkeeping Coach: James Blanchard\n* Head of Youth Development: Kevin Stewart\n* Sports Therapist: Andrea McIntosh\n* Sports Therapist: Rachel Mair\n* Kit Man: Lenny Binnie\n{{col-2}}\n\n===Club Management===\n* Chairman: Jim Mair<ref>[https://www.deveronvale.co.uk/copy-of-backroom-profiles Deveronvale FC Directors], ''Deveronvale Football Club'', 7 January 2019, Accessed 7 January 2019</ref>\n* Board of Directors:\n** Fergus Beaton\n** Peter Bruce\n** Linda Montgomery\n** Neil Montgomery\n* Executive Secretary: Stewart McPherson\n* Commercial Director: Calum Lawrie<ref>[https://www.deveronvale.co.uk/single-post/2019/01/06/Vale-Appoint-Commercial-Manager Vale appoint Commercial Manager], ''Deveronvale Football Club'', 6 January 2019, Accessed 7 January 2019</ref>\n{{col-end}}\n\n==Honours==\n* '''[[Highland Football League]]''': [[2002\u201303 Highland Football League|2002\u201303]], [[2005\u201306 Highland Football League|2005\u201306]]\n* '''[[Aberdeenshire Cup]]''': 1947\u201348, 1950\u201351, 1951\u201352, 1961\u201362, 1965\u201366, 2000\u201301, 2006\u201307, 2011\u201312\n* '''[[Aberdeenshire Shield]]''': 1994\u201395, 2002\u201303\n* '''[[Scottish Qualifying Cup|Scottish Qualifying Cup (North)]]''': 1951\u201352, 2001\u201302\n* '''Bells Cup (East)''': 1977\u201378\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n* [http://www.deveronvale.co.uk Official website]\n\n{{Highland Football League}}\n\n[[Category:Football clubs in Scotland]]\n[[Category:Highland Football League teams]]\n[[Category:Deveronvale F.C.| ]]\n[[Category:Association football clubs established in 1938]]\n[[Category:1938 establishments in Scotland]]\n[[Category:Sport in Aberdeenshire]]\n[[Category:Aberdeenshire]]\n[[Category:Banff, Aberdeenshire|Banff]]\n", "name_user": "Ross